<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1908264/annotation">共<span property="v:count">5</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="25587529">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1201616/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1201616-25.jpg" alt="丁丁" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25587529/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25587529/" class="">第147页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1201616/" class=" " title="丁丁">丁丁</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25587529">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在走向雪耻的民族自决的政治斗争中，民族主义话语几乎无可避免地走向极端，走向偏见，成为一种偏执的、反自由的意识形态，一种惟我独尊的、整体性的、道德上无限制的民族主义。
还是内部碾压异己的工具</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25587529/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-05 14:12</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在走向雪耻的民族自决的政治斗争中，民族主义话语几乎无可避免地走向极端，走向偏见，成为一种偏执的、反自由的意识形态，一种惟我独尊的、整体性的、道德上无限制的民族主义。</q></blockquote>
还是内部碾压异己的工具
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







